Fri Jun 19 17:52:04 UTC 2026 - Martin Pluskal <mpluskal@suse.com>

- Initial package, version 1.19.27
- mihomo (formerly Clash.Meta) is the actively maintained successor to
  the archived Dreamacro/clash; this package obsoletes both clash and
  clash-meta
